						<summary>

						<p>This is dated <hi rend="bold">Śaka 981, Hēmaḷambi</hi> with no further detailes. Hēmaḷambi corresponded to Śaka 980 current = <hi rend="bold">A.D. 1057-58.</hi> It belongs to the reign of the <hi rend="bold">Chōḷa</hi> king Kō-Parakēsaripanmar <hi rend="bold">Vijayarājēndra-Chōḷadēva</hi> and records that <hi rend="bold">Bammarasa,</hi> son of <hi rend="bold">Kōvarmarasa</hi> of <hi rend="bold">Champūru</hi> in <hi rend="bold">Maḍambūr twelve,</hi> fought against a great army and went to heaven.</p>						

						</summary>
